text: Tera Lents (April 14, 1982 - January 13, 2016), better known by her stage name Tera Wray, was an American pornographic actress. She appeared in around 25 adult movies between 2007 and 2014. Wray was born in Louisville, Kentucky. She was married to Wayne Static from 2008 until his death in 2014. Wray died on January 13, 2016 in California, aged 33.
